with version stable 1.70.0 1.50.0 1.11.0 1.10.0
with base    Python crossfire-maps curl libXaw libpng perl
#     with also --enable-static=no
with role    game
with trait   x11
with source  $SOURCEFORGE_URL crossfire/crossfire-$VERSION/crossfire-$VERSION.tar.gz
#   source $SOURCEFORGE_URL crossfire/crossfire-server/$VERSION/crossfire-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    last 20120329
with info    home http://crossfire.real-time.com/
with info    cite 'server for a multi-player graphical multi user dungeon combat type game
crossfire is a multi-player graphical
arcade and adventure game made for X.
It has certain flavours from other games,
especially Gauntlet and the rogue-like
games (Nethack, Moria, Angband, and Ragnarok).
Any number of players can move around in their own window, 
finding and using items and battling monsters.
They can choose to cooperate or compete in the same world.'

build(){
 unset CFLAGS CXXFLAGS LDFLAGS
 default_build
}

